Package com.sun.tools.visualvm.tools.jmx

JMX support in VisualVM.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CachedMBeanServerConnection Cached MBeanServerConnection:
JvmMXBeans MXBean proxies for the Java platform MXBeans.
MBeanCacheListener Interface for listeners of MBean cache events.
MBeanCacheOperations MBean cache operations.
 

Class Summary
CachedMBeanServerConnectionFactory The CachedMBeanServerConnectionFactory class is a factory class that allows to get instances of CachedMBeanServerConnection for a given MBeanServerConnection or JmxModel.
JmxModel This class encapsulates the JMX functionality of the target Java application.
JmxModelFactory The JmxModelFactory class is a factory class for getting the JmxModel representation for the Application.
JvmMXBeansFactory The JvmMXBeansFactory class is a factory class that allows to get instances of JvmMXBeans for a given MBeanServerConnection or JmxModel.
 

Enum Summary
JmxModel.ConnectionState Values for the ConnectionState bound property.
